name: N-SFW.COM Kakegurui
description: The N-SFW.COM plugin is an innovative extension for your Mue that automatically creates background images from the anime: Kakegurui from the N-SFW.COM platform. With an impressive collection of high-quality images, this plugin transforms your Mue into a visual experience and provides constantly changing, appealing backgrounds.
author: MaximilianGT500
